&lt;h3 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#prerequisites" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>You have created a &lt;a href="https://console.cloud.google.com/">GCP account&lt;/a>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>You have access to the Gardener dashboard and have permissions to create projects.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="steps">Steps&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#steps" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Go to the Gardener dashboard and create a &lt;em>Project&lt;/em>.&lt;/p>
 &lt;img src="https://gardener.cloud/__resources/new-gardener-project_077542.png">
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Check which roles are required by Gardener.&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Choose &lt;em>Secrets&lt;/em>, then the plus icon &lt;img src="https://gardener.cloud/__resources/plus-icon_9d16d6.png"> and select &lt;em>GCP&lt;/em>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>